snippet.textDisplay:
Score: Singing 10/10 Composition 10/10 Overall 10/10. Shairz's Season Score: A-, 4.0/5 

So many, so many memories just flood in, after hearing Rafaqat Jee voice who sang one of most beloved song, "Maula, Maula" from "Awarapan" (2007). Nothing can be said about this song, everything was top notch. Coke Studio is literally biding adieu leaving us in tears. Thank you Shiraz Uppal for bringing so much talent in Cs9. We won't see you as music director again, but we do hope to see you as a performer in many seasons ahead.
